Changes in version 0.99.2 (2021-10-06)
+ Changed the spike_metadata interface in the SparseDOSSA2 function. 
  spike_metadata can now be either character ("none" the default,
  "abundance", "prevalence", or "both", same as before), or a data.frame
  configuring the metadata-microbe associations (replacing the old
  feature_metadata_spike_df parameter)
+ More detailed documentation for these parameters
+ Better checking and error reporting for metadata spike-in user errors